Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.48,0:01:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs24\fad(150,100)}制作 十六夜 ？ 秋月 cunhan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3\fade(200,200)}红之密使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面 来确认决议的议题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下蒙古鲁来犯 帕罗也正值第二次黑龙战役
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿古纳亚国王博鲁格·巴联
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求沿海州六国出动海军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在还有自己的意见的话请发表
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,议长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博鲁格·巴联大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果放任蒙古鲁不管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的魔掌绝对会伸向世界贸易中心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我们沿海州联盟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须将蒙古鲁的威胁消灭在萌芽之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要战的话只能趁现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他想要发言的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱果鲁市长 昂达姆斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有想要说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真心话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说博鲁格大人您认为我有非说不可的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经和蒙古鲁的人密谈过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敬了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么进行表决
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员一致表决通过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿海州为阻止蒙古鲁的侵略、帮助帕罗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同意出兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能采纳这项提案 我表示衷心的感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那老狐狸获胜般的表情是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有问题 与蒙古鲁有关的阴谋有关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在长期的会议之后 我宣告巴联会议结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是庆祝宣战的庆贺酒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿海州参战了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次战争整个中原 不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将演变成牵连全世界的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以更加不能错过这次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样我都要亲手抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人真是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了些无聊的事情沸腾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开战之后像我们这些弱者只会被践踏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那些都不认识的国王和公主的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为你会狂喜乱舞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却突然显出一副寂寞的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有喜欢的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么丢下她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又为什么是一个人 弥丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心上人发誓要和永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却死在海上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 伊修特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要去吗 这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是红色佣兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥丽亚 你是个好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里 别让他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带回去让他从实招来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能放过他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 挺住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.89,0:06:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是佣兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佣兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这个就拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送到蒙古鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说蒙古鲁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 把这个送到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报酬随你开价
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 帮你送
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要给我信物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让对方知道是你雇佣了我的凭证
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙古鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许 这才是我通往宝座的阶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 事态正在急速恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在马尔加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发表了夺回帕罗宣言的卢南周围聚集了五千
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在萨拉埃姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达路贡和达巴鲁斯身边聚集了七千
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在达纳姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利纳斯聚集了超过八千士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如纳利斯大人说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这三股部队会师的话就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要在此前出兵摧毁他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是若是为此导致库里斯塔鲁守备薄弱也很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要召回驻守尤诺的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么卡斯隆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你率领黑骑士队去镇压反叛军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我难以从命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是库里斯塔鲁的警卫官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个职务没有被撤销
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让身为警卫官的我去镇压地方叛乱有点不合理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳利斯大人预料到了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在这三个地方发起叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁机夺回守备薄弱的库里斯塔鲁宫殿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那么布鲁克 涅隆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们能去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且派快马去尤诺 请求援兵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我就此告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想不到那个小心翼翼的卡斯隆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有靠山居然也敢违抗长官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话 是叛变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会安排部下暗中监视他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个乡巴佬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡斯隆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是纳利斯大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你已经相当熟悉魔道之都了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡斯隆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么镇压反叛军的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由布鲁克和涅隆前去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找回尤诺的部队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那道命令是传不到尤诺了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也要加紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要尽全力为我办事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没变节吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一代发迹的蒙古鲁需要什么忠诚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样告诉我的不是正纳利斯大人您吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今后我该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后指令就来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由丽姬亚小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡卢大人和贝克公爵行踪不明？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后收到的消息是他们正前往鞑念湿地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就渺无音讯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么在我的出征之时不要将斯卡卢军计算在内
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起 我那个没有规矩的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这回事 斯塔克王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 能出征的阿鲁古斯正规军总数三万
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 有三万五千吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么明天请允许我出征
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:12:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后我率领的都是从别国借来的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是进入库里斯塔鲁的都城之时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先头部队要全部是我的军队了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺回库里斯塔鲁的不是阿鲁古斯军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷姆斯·阿卢多罗斯四世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你明白这点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后没有我的许可严禁私自联系纳利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕罗的国王是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳利斯也只不过是我的一个臣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的帕罗之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的帕罗魔道士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都必须而且只能向我一人宣誓效忠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铭记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:12:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个有趣的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初你就像是个受惊乱哭的雏鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着旅途延续
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同朝日驱散黑暗一般 你发生了明显的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕今后也会继续改变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运之丝就是这样编织的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是随着命运之神亚安的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与你可能成为敌人亦或是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.12,0:13:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:14:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来了 有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会变成什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确你不是泛泛之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因 今后也请给我出谋划策
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果需要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙古鲁雇佣的刺客吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是奇塔伊的纹章
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇塔伊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙古鲁雇佣了奇塔伊的暗杀者了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太子殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕的人就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有愿与我斯卡卢生死与共的人跟上来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要翻越威廉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太子殿下 无论去何处我都追随您
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡卢大人 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁古斯 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡卢真是拥有一帮好部下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝克公爵不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手是人类的话 我倒是从未害怕过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对手是大山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡卢大人也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么意外 可怕的东西就可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 只有前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝克公爵 别死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 咱们都是有心爱的女人的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走散了 里·花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷姆斯 祝你武运昌隆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.68,0:16:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔父 感谢你帮了我那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才见到你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经又到分别的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾玛姨妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿胜利女神伊拉娜向你微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿亚努斯保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚努斯肯定再让我们重逢的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豹战士奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后他们俩也拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出征
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着帕罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 阿鲁古斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 我的幼年时光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都离我远去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:18:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修特邦也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷姆斯也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且 总有一天奎因也会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终我的身边 什么人都...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏妮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是给蒙古鲁的密信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这封密信关系着蒙古鲁和帕罗的存亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个交换蒙古鲁的贵族身份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都该倒找我钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有忘记什么关键的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修特邦 有什么关键的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马鲁斯伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果万一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的通缉画像被四处张贴的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做的事可真够蠢的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有别的国家为这个东西出更高的价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 弥丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到一匹好马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了你不少的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的亲切我不会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 伊修特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 帮上你的忙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先说好 我不是喜欢上你才帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得你会就这样走上灭亡的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确我也被称为召来灾祸的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 以多鲁的硫磺吐息之名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有能缠上本大爷的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的男人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要过问我的私事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:21:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是蒙古鲁的纹章
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是奸细
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追 别让他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 他不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 他说过自己是召来灾祸的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不恨他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我的心上人一样 有大海的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修特邦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会惊讶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自起程离开的我 作为帕罗的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在库里斯塔鲁迎接琳达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经追过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.32,0:22:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以风之达贡(执掌风、水、雷的神)之名
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可事关未来伟大王者的性命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:24:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜在的激情洋溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被丝线操纵的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.57,0:24:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倾倒于狂乱之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.73,0:24:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将思念注入高举的宝剑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.47,0:24:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 反击的狼烟冉冉升起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.07,0:24:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 库里斯塔鲁的叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.18,0:24:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在亚安的指引下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:22:56.67,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}This is my road 導かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:23:04.81,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}Here I stand ここにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:11.79,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}父と母の 遠い面影（記憶）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:19.97,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}瞳閉じれば 聞こえる声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:30.03,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}This is my road 歩いてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.79,0:23:38.38,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}果たしない時もう越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.58,0:23:44.39,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}This is my life 扉を開け
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.60,0:23:55.38,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}定め（運命）と共に 今、道（伝説）を刻んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:22:56.67,ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}这是我的道路 被指引着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:23:04.81,ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}你依然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:11.79,ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}父母渐渐消逝的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:19.97,ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}闭上眼睛依然可闻的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:30.03,ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}这是我的道路 大步向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.79,0:23:38.38,ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}无尽岁月已经度过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.58,0:23:44.39,ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}这是我的生活 大门向我敞开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.60,0:23:55.38,ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}与命运一起 现在开辟新的道路
